author: jleroux
msg: A patch from Chirag Manocha "Out Parameter showing under In Parameter head for createAcctgTransAndEntries service reference." (https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OFBIZ-2917) - OFBIZ-2917
In service createAcctgTransAndEntries, there is no need to IN acctgTranId. It is required as OUT parameter. So behavior should be overridden instead of defining acctgTransId again.
